- [ ] Optimistic category save — show the pill instantly on click (client-side
      lookup of category id -> {name, color} built from the same list already
      rendered for the picker), save in background, reconcile/rollback on
      response. Fixes "the refresh gets in the way."
- [ ] Replace the flat category <select> (transactions.blade.php ~713-718) with
